OL,3,CArmed murderers face life in jail
OL,4,Cafter axe attack on DPD driver
OL,6,FTheir trial came after four men -
OL,7,FArshdeep Singh, Jagdeep Singh,
OL,8,FShivdeep Singh and Manjot Singh - were
OL,9,Flast year convicted of Aurman's murder.
OL,11,FA fifth man, Sukhmandeep Singh, was
OL,12,Fconvicted of manslaughter after acting
OL,13,Fas the 'inside man' at the DPD depot
OL,14,Fin Stoke-on-Trent where Aurman worked
OL,15,Fand passing information on to the
OL,16,Fothers.
OL,18,FThey were locked up for more than 120
OL,19,Fyears in April 2024.
