OL,3,CArmed murderers face life in jail
OL,4,Cafter axe attack on DPD driver
OL,6,FJurors heard how DPD worker Aurman was
OL,7,Fkilled in Berwick Avenue, Shrewsbury,
OL,8,Fon August 21 2023.
OL,10,FHe was 'chopped in the head' with an
OL,11,Faxe, which fractured his skull and
OL,12,F'exposed' his brain, leaving onlookers
OL,13,Fhorrified.
OL,15,FThe 23-year-old was also 'clubbed'
OL,16,Fover the head with a golf club with
OL,17,Fsuch force that its head broke off and
OL,18,Fthe shaft was bent.
OL,20,FA knife wound to his back cut through
OL,21,Fone of his ribs.
