OL,6,FThey managed to flee the UK following
OL,7,FAurman's murder and were eventually
OL,8,Fdetained in Austria last year.
OL,10,FJudge Simon Hirst thanked jurors for
OL,11,Ftheir attention to the case after the
OL,12,Fverdicts were delivered.
OL,14,FDue to the 'distressing' details
OL,15,Fheard, he told them that they would be
OL,16,Fexcused from serving as jurors in the
OL,17,Ffuture.
OL,19,FHe said: "The law is a matter for me,
OL,20,Fthe facts are a matter for you.
